1. Arduino Nano(Recommended - Small Footprint), or Uno, or Mega

2. AS5600 with diametrically magnetized magnet

3. All 3d Printed Parts

4. 775 Motor shaft on both side

5. BTS7960B


// Unnecessary if using custom mounting options with motor snd the pendulum!

6. Flange Shaft Coupling 2 pcs

7. M6 x 250mm threaded or unthreaded rod

8. Mass for Rod - used a stepper motor in my case
